target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_SEQ_00<tab>Halbnix scheint mit seinen Repa<var 16 /var>ratur<var 16 /var>arbei<var 16 /var>ten nicht weiterzukommen.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_SEQ_01<tab>It seems the Idyllshire aetheryte may be growing unstable, and is in need of a proper inspection. However, Halfsix lacks the necessary aetherflow distributors to make his analysis. As with many things in the burgeoning settlement, it appears these, too, are located somewhere within the Arkhitekton. Thus, Halfsix bids that you make your way there and search the Illuminati pots for three of these tools.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_SEQ_01<tab>Halbnix will den Ätheryten reparieren, aber ihm fehlt <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8B20020202 /var> dazu. Geh zu <var 32 ((EObj)) 03F61E9B75020402 /var> im Arkhitekton und bring ihm, was er braucht.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_SEQ_02<tab>You obtain three aetherflow distributors, and dispatch a number of Illuminati as well. Return with them to Halfsix in Idyllshire now.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_SEQ_02<tab>Du hast <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8B20020502 /var> besorgt. Bring die Ersatzteile gleich zu Halbnix.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_SEQ_03<tab>Halfsix expresses his gratitude for your service. The aetheryte will no doubt continue to spin in Idyllshire for many years to come, thanks to your efforts.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_SEQ_03<tab>Halbnix hat alles dankend in Empfang genommen. Die Ätheryten-Technologie wurde in Sharlayan entwickelt und ist nun nicht mehr aus Eorzea wegzudenken.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_TODO_00<tab>Search Illuminati pots for aetherflow distributors within the Arkhitekton.
TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the aetherflow distributors to Halfsix.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_TODO_01<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8B20020502 /var>)) /var> zu Halbnix in Frohehalde bringen

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_000<tab>Pshkohhh... Halfsix has very important task for trusty uplander, must be done with fastness!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_000<tab>Kho! Großwachsene<var 08 E905 (()) ((r)) /var> ist Rettenring in Not!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_001<tab>Aetheryte of Idyllshire needs of inspection, maybe needs upkeep too. If gobbies do not take a look and fix little problems, its spinnings may shudder and stop─or there is very big boom! But Halfsix does not have the right tools...
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_001<tab>Halbnix muss Ätherschicken-Stein reparieren, aber fehlen wichtige Ersetzenteile.
... Dunkel in Denkschale? Benutzzu doch auch immer, für Ätherschicken an ferne Ort!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_002<tab>Uplander, there is no time to waste! Halfsix needs aetherflow distributors. The nearest are in base of Illuminati! Come, come, raid their store pots!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_002<tab>In Werkenstatt Arkhitekton gibt alle Sachen für Reparieren. Kannzu bringen Dreistück <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E8B20030202 /var> aus <var 32 ((EObj)) 06F61E9B75020402 /var>?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_010<tab>Hurry, uplander! Aetherflow distributors are somewhere in the Arkhitekton!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_010<tab>In Werkenstatt Arkhitekton gibt alle Sachen für Reparieren. Kannzu bringen Dreistück <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E8B20030202 /var> aus <var 32 ((EObj)) 06F61E9B75020402 /var>?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_021<tab>Pshkohhh... Thank you, uplander! With these, Halfsix can do upkeep!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_021<tab>Kho, Großestein fallen von Herz von Halbnix. Jetzt können alle bald wieder weitschicken in Äther. Alte Ätherschicken-Stein ist fährlich, kannzu Weg verlieren in Äther.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_022<tab>Uplanders of Sharlayan are making aetherytes to whirl, using tricksy ancient knowings. If gobbieflock uses tools and parts left by old uplanders, then aetheryte of Idyllshire will stay spinning for many, many years!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ815_01945_HALFSIX_000_022<tab>Ätherschicken-Stein ist Findung von alte Sharlayan. Sehr praktisch, kho!
